{"tid":1764462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民驗證黃藍真偽 - 黃色經濟圈新副本！！！","createTime":"2019-12-01T06:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T08:33:54.000Z","uid":298995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f4ccc953b06c099d5eb199130d9afbda610ea82","tid":1764462,"uid":298995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:33:42.000Z","msg":"繼之前出 PO 話俾大家聽 Explorit 地圖指南公開測試之後，<br />\nExplorit 黃藍指標而家公開收集大家報料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講多無謂，先去圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j49Rd20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj49Rd20.png&h=455d199e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MiAH49H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMiAH49H.png&h=89b9657c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無從入手？唔知點開始？<br />\n準備埋攻略俾你地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H66wd22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH66wd22.png&h=ce71ab39&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NaV80H0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNaV80H0.png&h=b8ff3883&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MsYZnWm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMsYZnWm.png&h=706e630d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n禁入黎開始打副本啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://app.explorit.co\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.explorit.co&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=3db7c608\" target=\"_blank\">https://app.explorit.co</a> <br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n可以透露既資料係，<br />\n我地之後會用算法歸納大家提供既鋪頭資料，<br />\n得出一個黃藍指標評分顯示出黎俾大家睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要會基於以下因素： <br />\n1．投票數目 <br />\n2．提交資料質量 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2．黃藍有效既資料數目 <br />\n3．日期 <br />\n4．提供資料用戶是否經過認可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於詳細點計就唔可以講啦，講左出黎俾你地刷仲得了既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但到最尾都係要人提交資料我地先可以做落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以<br />\n副本要人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陸續黎緊既係功能仲有： <br />\n1。黃藍驗證開放即時上載圖片功能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （遲下俾你寫埋鋪頭評語同食評又點話）<br />\n2。全自動回報新黃藍店鋪系統，加鋪頭唔駛再有 Lag Time<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地知道好多人都想係一隻 App，<br />\n而家已經做緊前期功夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地既開發考慮都係點樣係幫到擴大黃色經濟圈先 ！<br />\n鋪頭而家可能都仲係餐廳為主，<br />\n但係我地已經執緊其他類型鋪頭既資料，遲下就會放到上去 ～ <br />\n<br />\n想知Update 可以 Follow 左我地先：<br />\nIG -- <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explorithk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fexplorithk&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=e579df47\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/explorithk</a><br />\nFB -- <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/explorithk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fexplorithk&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=e2c1de1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/explorithk</a> <br />\n呢兩者除左 Stories 之外基本上會同步 Update <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n若果有意見既話可以 TG 俾我地 @exploritapp<br />\n會盡快覆大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n擴大黃色經濟圈！！！"},{"pid":"c432b01fd4462f346e24d81e914fcf4256b13f60","tid":1764462,"uid":298995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:33:54.000Z","msg":"【直播】「毋忘初心尖沙咀大遊行」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1764480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1764480</a><br />\n<br />\n先推呢個，出面要人！"}]}